name: in_range
description: Returns true if the provided date is contained in the provided date_range.
examples:
FROM employees
| WHERE IN_RANGE(hire_date, TO_DATE_RANGE("1985-02-01..1985-03-01"))
| KEEP emp_no, hire_date
| SORT emp_no
